<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The regex for method name validation in "Zend_Json_Server_Request" schould look like "protected $<em>methodRegex = '/^[a-z][a-z0-9</em>.]<em>$/i';" instead of "protected $<em>methodRegex = '/^[a-z][a-z0-9</em>]</em>$/i';" in order to support dotted namespaces, which are supported by some JSON-RPC-Clients for JavaScript yet.</p>

